# textdomain: mcl_clock
Clocks are tools which shows the current time of day in the Overworld.=Ure so orodja, ki prikazujejo trenutni čas dneva na Površju.

The clock contains a rotating disc with a sun symbol (yellow disc) and moon symbol and a little “pointer” which shows the current time of day by estimating the real position of the sun and the moon in the sky. Noon is represented by the sun symbol and midnight is represented by the moon symbol.=Ura vsebuje vrteči se disk s simbolom sonca (rumen disk) in simbolom lune ter majhen „kazalec“, ki prikazuje trenutni čas dneva z oceno dejanskega položaja sonca in lune na nebu. Poldne predstavlja simbol sonca, polnoč pa simbol lune.

Displays the time of day in the Overworld=Prikazuje čas dneva na Površju
Clock=Ura